FluxIndex Technical Specifications

System Requirements:
- .NET 9.0 or higher
- Entity Framework Core 9.0
- SQLite 3.40+ or PostgreSQL 13+
- OpenAI API access (optional)

Architecture Overview:
The FluxIndex library implements a layered architecture with clear separation of concerns. The core domain models are independent of external dependencies, while infrastructure services provide concrete implementations.

Performance Benchmarks:
- Document Indexing: 1000 docs/second
- Search Latency: <50ms average
- Memory Usage: <100MB for 10K documents
- Storage Efficiency: 90% compression ratio

API Specifications:
The FluxIndex SDK provides a simple fluent API for common operations. Advanced users can access lower-level services for fine-grained control.

Quality Assurance:
All components include comprehensive unit tests, integration tests, and performance benchmarks. The library follows industry best practices for security and reliability.